race.description: Senator Ken Maddy S. Presented By Breeders' Cup Charities Stakes
race.comment: PURO MAGIC (7) scored first up at Niigata then finished 3 lengths away in eighth over 1200m in the G1 Sprinters Stakes at Nakayama. Unbeaten in two starts at the third run in so she is sure to feature in the finish. QUEEN MAXIMA (4) finished sixth in the G3 Green Flash Handicap at this track (Turf) over this distance last time out. Has a strong record at this trip, scoring two times from four starts. Drawn to enjoy a nice trail just off the pace. Likely to feature. SHOOT IT TRUE (6) reunites with Luan Machado after scoring with ease over 1106m at Saratoga (Turf) last time. Likely to push forward and race on the pace. Winning claims on best figures. SUNGLOW (5) scored last start at Santa Anita (Turf) to make it two wins from three starts this campaign. Has the gate speed to take up a forward position. In the mix.
